title: The Mafia - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 6/2/22

description:
George Noory and author Michael Franzese discuss his life as a member of the Colombo crime family, how the mob tries to exploit corrupt politicians, and if the mafia is as powerful today as it was in the past.
